title: TTC - Great Authors of the Western Literary Tradition, 1st Editi
description:
From Usenet. This one is completely different from the second edition and uses other professors - including Michael Sugrue, Arnold Weinstein and S. Georgia Nugent.

Note #1 - Although it is divided into parts that each start with a Lecture 1 (akin to Great Minds, 2nd Edition), I made it into one album, that is the way I find most convenient, although opinions might differ.
Note #2 - Part 2 of the guidebook is missing
